when you're confronted to this

00:13:41.480 --> 00:13:46.290
in your life, how you live
through that, if you can,

00:13:46.290 --> 00:13:51.180
because a lot of Chagossians
didn't go through it.

00:13:51.180 --> 00:13:55.550
A lot of them committed
suicide and it was very,

00:13:55.550 --> 00:13:57.250
very hard for their population.

00:13:57.250 --> 00:14:00.520
